doc.title: Heartbeat
doc.plot: Constable Nick Rowan is a English Policeman in the 1960's who decides to be reassigned to the same small village where he was evacuated to during World War II as a child. There, he patrols the countryside as a part of a small attachment in the area dealing with the various events and problems that come up while at same time keeping a eye on Claude Greengrass, the local rogue.
